{"tid":1941082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"又語出驚人！ 陳柏惟拋邀香港人來台當兵","createTime":"2020-03-24T07:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T10:53:43.000Z","uid":29188,"like":46,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"a77783fc90699d730c36f38ff1f57a38e782083f","tid":1941082,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:51:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2020-03-24 11:48 聯合報 記者周志豪／台北即時報導</span><br />\n<br />\n香港反送中事件引發國內民眾關心支持，不少人更主張「今日香港、明日台灣」，提升台港互動親密度。台灣基進立委陳柏惟上午在立院質詢時建議，政府應邀香港人來台灣當兵。行政院長蘇貞昌則回應，「這個我看可能要更慎重」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6yd3tS3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yd3tS3.jpg&h=1e28bb13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">陳柏惟表示，讓香港人來台灣當兵有三大好處，第一他們比我們年輕，第二他們更討厭中國...</span><br />\n<br />\n陳柏惟表示，讓香港人來台灣當兵有三大好處，第一他們比我們年輕，第二他們更討厭中國，第三可增加台灣勞工人數。蘇貞昌則說，「他們爭取自由民主我們是很關心」，但是否要讓香港人來台當兵，「這個我看可能要更慎重」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6656/4439024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6656%2F4439024&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=1f0f2ddc\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6656/4439024</a>"},{"pid":"684f28439fe207322eac139b8a0ceff65d6a6141","tid":1941082,"uid":140924,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第二他們更討厭中國</blockquote><br />\nTRUE <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e73db40a732b546f0b705cf93c9a0cd8f28a27","tid":1941082,"uid":74622,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:54:38.000Z","msg":"陳柏惟提「找港人來台當兵」 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1940946/page/4\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1940946/page/4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9e8f4b80e40b91e2cab9e6541d3a18e445fc24","tid":1941082,"uid":125582,"like":0,"dislike":